entries.journal_entry_description: A group of mercenaries, the Strehkforce, have taken the security beacon. Go get it back.
entries.journal_entry_title: Get the Security Beacon Back from the Mercenaries
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Stehkforce before looking for the beacon.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Strehkforce leaders, and the Strehkforce will become less of a threat.
entries.task02_task_display_string_1: Defeat Evan Strehk, a Strehkforce commander
entries.task02_task_display_string_2: Defeat Maris Fahrs, a Strehkforce commander
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Find the Security Beacon in the Strehkforce base.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Vance Groten with the recovered security beacon.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Return to Professor Hudmasse and let him know you have a security beacon for Stonewall Labs.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Assault the Strehkforce by attacking Strehkforce soldiers.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Attack the Strehkforce by fighting Strehkforce mercenaries.
